  <brief_title>Safety of Phenylephrine for Oral Mucositis Prevention</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Safety Study of Phenylephrine Applied Topically to the Oral Mucosa in Cancer Patients Receiving Radiation to Sub-mandibular Lymph Nodes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
