  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if applying the drug phenylephrine to the inside of
      the mouth can be done safely and is tolerable to use in cancer patients receiving radiation
      to the Sub-mandibular lymph nodes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
